<br />
To conclude this article, I wanted to let all of you know that the game has lost none of its glory. Even though we dont have new sets to buy or large 200+ player tournaments to play in. The game is still just as awesome as it ever was. I welcome you back to the game that continues to grow and change having been lost by its creator years and years ago. Please feel open to ask me any question over dmail or visit the PC website and start getting involved on the message boards. I hope this has been an informative tool for you on your quest back to glory. <br />
<br />
Thanks for reading, and remember current players, this wasnt for you. <br />
